    <criterion testable="true">Render verification (FR-DV-04 Acceptance): chart renders date + event title + days-from-now (e.g., `May 28 / Pre-trial hearing · in 3d`); expand opens upcoming events list.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">TASK-INDEX.md shows 033 as ✅ completed.</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>

  <notes>
    FR-DV-04 does NOT specify a sprk_optionsjson payload — the spec only lists Visual Type + Entity + Data + Drill Through. The DueDateCard visual type already exists and handles its display contract internally. If the sprk_chartdefinition schema requires a non-null sprk_optionsjson, default to `{}` unless the existing DueDateCard chart defs (per the inventory from task 001) reveal a different convention.

    Per Phase A.5 recon (spec.md §Assumptions), `sprk_event` fields are assumed `sprk_regardingmatter`, `sprk_finalduedate`, `sprk_eventstatus`. Task 003 verifies; use task 003 output.
  </notes>

